data.description: Are you looking for a 5 bed house for less than 500k? Here it is! This 5 bed-3 full bath home is located just north of HWY 512. Split level home, built in 2006 on a huge, fully fenced lot. Upstairs you'll find 3 beds & 2 baths, dining room and galley kitchen. Sliding door access to the upper deck as well. Downstairs has the second family room, 2 more bedrooms, 1 full bath, utility room and rear yard access. Owners bedroom is upstairs with a large walk in closet and full bath.  The house sits off the street to allow for additional street parking. Come make this house your new home! Short drive to JBLM & Tacoma.
